snippet.title: Party Hard 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign-up for the alpha - http://partyhard.game

You don't get your Christmas bonus, so the only logical thing to do is massacre everyone at a corporate party. The sequel to 2015's Party Hard is coming THIS SUMMER! Tell us what you think about the new look in the comments below.
